---
title: One-Pan Beef Meatballs with Tomato & Bacon Risoni
description: Fuss-free is the name of this dinner game with these cheesy, tender meatballs that are cooked in a simple tomato sauce. Everything is cooked in the same big frying pan, meaning less washing up for you, and more rich, Italian flavours for the whole family – it's a win win!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b63dd7d30006c0390155077-fb3b6e7e.jpg
